    <h1>Companies</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>On this page of the manual you will learn everything about how to manage companies in plentymarkets. You manage companies in the <strong>CRM » Companies</strong> menu. You can, among others, <a href="#create-company">create</a>, <a href="#search-company">search</a> and <a href="#edit-company">edit</a> companies and <a href="#link-company-with-contact">link contacts with the company</a>.</p>
</div>
