<h2 id="create-company">1. Creating a company</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The user interface to create a new company allows a high degree of flexibility for positioning content and data. This works by intuitively positioning areas for content and elements on the dashboard via drag-and-drop. Each area and each element can be further edited by clicking on <span class="icon "><i class="psicon-design_inline_edit"></i></span>. <a href="#table-functions-editing-mode">Table 1</a> contains an overview on the functions available in the editing mode of company data record.</p>
