<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Creating a company:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>CRM » Companies</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the left side on <span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-plus  "></i></span> <strong>Add new company</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the data or select the options from the drop-down lists. Note <a href="#table-create-company">Table 2</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon "><i class="material-save"></i></span>) the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
